Invocation Name: chuck jokes
des:
Did you know that Chuck Norris doesn't eat honey, but bees directly?
This skill lets you discover more than 80 fun facts about the great Chuck Norris.
A skill suitable for adults.
Just ask him a fact and Alexa will respond instantly.

This skill is not meant to be a mockery and is nothing official about Chuck Norris.
This skill does not memorize any user data, it shares nothing with third parties.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
